data.description: ****Sellers have received multiple offers and calling for highest and best by Sunday 3/6/22 at 1pm****Wonderful townhome w/ attached garage in highly sought-after Indian Land walking distance to restaurants, bars, shopping, grocery and more!  Open floor plan features wood floors, 9’ ceilings, upgraded kitchen and large master suite.  Upgrade kitchen boasts granite countertops, tile backsplash, large island w/ breakfast bar, pantry, & stainless-steel appliances including refrigerator and microwave.  Master bedroom features tray ceilings w/ ceiling fan, large walk-in closet & Master bathroom with double vanity and separate shower & soaking tub.  Laundry on 2nd floor next to all bedrooms with included washer and dryer. Just minutes to Ballantyne, historic downtown Waxhaw, 485 & 77.
